We use the lemma `AnalyticOnNhd.intervalIntegrable_log_norm` which is available in the imported Value Distribution library (or standard extensions thereof for Nevanlinna theory). We also use `hg.neg.add_const (f a)` to construct the analytic function `y ↦ f a - g y` from `hg`.

